# production
/build

# tina generated artifacts (rebuilt by `tinacms build`/`tinacms dev`)

# The Tina self-hosted backend indexes content from the LOCAL filesystem baked
# into the image at `tinacms build` time (the GitHub provider is only used for
# write-back/commits, NOT for reading content at runtime). So the content +
# assets the CMS edits MUST be tracked here, or the collection indexes 0 docs.
# Build-only Astro files (Page.astro, _shell, preset.ts) stay ignored.
/src/clients/blessing-marketing-od/*
!/src/clients/blessing-marketing-od/content/
!/src/clients/blessing-marketing-od/assets/

# misc
.DS_Store
.env
.env.local
.idea

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
